Text: Funny story...I found this CD for 99 cents in a delete bin back in the late 90's at a CD shop in Royal Oak, MI...I just liked the cover and took a chance on it...truly is a great CD and a lucky find!  Thanks for sharing/reminding me of this band again!!!
I vaguely remember this band name. Maybe I will recognize some of it when I listen to it. Thank you for continuing to post stuff

thnx my prayers were answered It maybe a small thing but for me this is incredible, you are one person who can put a smile on someone's face with your efforts and generosity. One more  request if you have wild garden by lions and ghost that would make my flashback to memory lane complete. Again thank you and god bless
